  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Aster Fpv is the Fpv Drone simulator including fps mode, play in multiplayer or alone</h2>Sneak between moving construction cranes.<br>Practice chasing cars. <br>Race solo or in multiplayer between buildings and natural obstacles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >** The new feature is the missions available on the fps mode **</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In Multiplayer</h2> - <i>Fps mode:</i> Compete with other players with a rocket launcher or a machine gun and complete missions.<br> - <i>Race mode:</i> Try to be the 1st or at the top of the ranking.<br> - <i>Free mode:</i> Explore the places and train to perfect your piloting level<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solo mode</h2> - <i>Race mode:</i> Try to beat your best time<br> - <i>Free mode:</i> Explore the places and practice your driving skills",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Aster Fpv is the Fpv Drone simulator including fps mode, play in multiplayer or alone</h2>Sneak between moving construction cranes.<br>Practice chasing cars. <br>Race solo or in multiplayer between buildings and natural obstacles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >** The new feature is the missions available on the fps mode **</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In Multiplayer</h2> - <i>Fps mode:</i> Compete with other players with a rocket launcher or a machine gun and complete missions.<br> - <i>Race mode:</i> Try to be the 1st or at the top of the ranking.<br> - <i>Free mode:</i> Explore the places and train to perfect your piloting level<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solo mode</h2> - <i>Race mode:</i> Try to beat your best time<br> - <i>Free mode:</i> Explore the places and practice your driving skills",
